rent.\\\"\", \"from\": 572, \"to\": 686, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their menu\", \"from\": 585, \"to\": 595}, {\"ngram\": \"every time\", \"from\": 622, \"to\": 632}, {\"ngram\": \"a little something\", \"from\": 656, \"to\": 674}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cafe Provence, which opened more than 20 years ago, and the French Market, which opened in 2013, offer French imports, vintage items, cookbooks and other French products.\", \"from\": 688, \"to\": 858, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 693, \"end\": 701, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Provence\", \"score\": 0.9999999391407092, \"rank\": 5.819760968775715e-08, \"text\": \"Provence\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Provence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Provence\"}, {\"begin\": 748, \"end\": 761, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Market\", \"score\": 0.9999999999974989, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French Market\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Market\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Market\"}, {\"begin\": 791, \"end\": 797, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9998562902625632, \"rank\": 0.0001368082063184235, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 842, \"end\": 848, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9998562902625632, \"rank\": 0.0001368082063184235, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"vintage items\", \"from\": 807, \"to\": 820}, {\"ngram\": \"cookbooks\", \"from\": 822, \"to\": 831}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Those are the things that we bring to the table because of who we are and where we come from,\\\