_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1664, \"end\": 1671, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Custard\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.428659712539052e-20, \"text\": \"Custard\", \"types\": [\"Q2095\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Custard\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Custard\"}, {\"begin\": 1679, \"end\": 1688, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brookside_High_School\", \"score\": 0.991567009603995, \"rank\": 0.008495009339670873, \"text\": \"Brookside\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3914\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brookside_High_School\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brookside_High_School\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A little further east\", \"from\": 1550, \"to\": 1571}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We really tried to do things the French way, which is simple but delicious and homemade and high quality,\\\"French Custardowner Jessica Wood said.\", \"from\": 1704, \"to\": 1849, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1831, \"end\": 1838, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Buchanan\", \"score\": 0.8323062559553221, \"rank\": 0.1352934525252756, \"text\": \"Jessica\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Buchanan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Buchanan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 1727, \"to\": 1733}, {\"ngram\": \"simple but delicious and homemade and high quality,\\\"French\", \"from\": 1759, \"to\": 1817}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I definitely feel like we will have a boost in sales this summer with people wanting to just try French custard.\\\"\", \"from\": 1850, \"to\": 1964, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1948, \"end\": 1954, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9998562902625632, \"rank\": 0.0001368082063184235, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbp